title: r/Idontworkherelady Entitled Karen Gets Punched In The Face!
description:
r/Idontworkherelady In today's episode, an entitled Karen in a supermarket tries to boss around another young lady who's shopping. The young lady isn't pay attention because... why would she? She doesn't work there, after all. The Karen rudely grabs the young woman, which startles the woman so she reflexively punches Karen in the face. Karen absolutely freaks out, of course, but the young woman is just fine because she was minded her own business when the Karen grabbed her.
